quran[8{c,v,t}:
16,80,"Allah ne tumahray liye tumahray gharon ko jaye sukoon banaya is ne janwaron ki khaalon se tumahray liye aisay makaan peda kiye jinhein tum safar aur qiyam, dono halaton mein halka paate ho uss ne janwaron ke sof aur oon aur balon se tumahray liye pahannay aur baratnay ki bohat si cheezein peda kar den jo zindagi ki muddat muqarara taq tumahray kaam aati hain"
16,81,"is ne apni peda ki hui bohat si cheezon se tumahray liye saaye ka intizam kya, pahoron mein tumahray liye panah gahin banayen, aur tumhe aisi poshakain bakhsheen jo tumhe garmi se bachati hain aur kuch doosri poshakain jo aapas ki jung mein tumhari hifazat karti hain is terhan woh tum par apni nematon ki takmeel karta hai shayad ke tum farmaa bardaar bano"
16,82,"ab agar yeh log mun morty hain to ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum par saaf saaf pegham haq pouncha dainay ke siwa aur koi zimma daari nahi hai"
16,83,"yeh Allah ke ahsaan ko pehchante hain, phir is ka inkaar karte hain aur inn mein besh tar log aisay hain jo haq maan-ne ke liye tayyar nahi hain"
16,84,"( aِnhin kuch hosh bhi hai ke uss roz kya banay gi ) jabkay hum har ummat mein se aik gawah khara karen ge, phir kafiroon ko nah hujjatain paish karne ka mauqa diya jaayegaa nah un se tauba o astaghfar hi ka mutalba kya jaye ga"
16,85,zalim log jab aik dafaa azaab dekh len ge to is ke baad nah unn ke azaab mein koi takhfeef ki jaye gi aur nah inhen aik lamha bhar ki mohlat di jaye gi
16,86,"aur jab woh log jinhon ne duniya mein shirk kya tha apne tehra-ay hue sharikon ko dekhen ge to kahin ge"" ae parvar-digaar, yahi hain hamaray woh shareek jinhein hum tujhe chore kar puraka karte thay"" is par unn ke woh mabood inhen saaf jawab den ge ke"" tum jhutay ho """
16,87,uss waqt yeh sab Allah ke agay jhuk jayen ge aur un ki woh saari aftara-pardaziyan )bohtan bazi) rafo chakkar ho jayen gi jo yeh duniya mein karte rahay thay
